{"tid":1969522,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"網紅網購母乳試喝嘔吐，還加了巧克力餅乾和麥片食用，母乳協會籲檢舉下架","createTime":"2020-04-12T13:03:13.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-12T13:50:21.000Z","uid":1886,"like":2,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"485d7cd37f055e37238e5c6b2b919836437cabef","tid":1969522,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-12T13:03:13.000Z","msg":"擁有148萬訂閱者的知名Youtuber小玉4月7日上傳一部影片「新鮮現榨!我喝了媽媽的人奶!?」，從網路購物平台訂購母乳試喝，中間數度嘔吐，還加了巧克力餅乾和麥片食用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。台灣母乳協會今（9）在臉書發文批評，「不該將關乎健康議題的母乳或者對辛苦哺餵、擠乳的哺乳媽媽拿來作為嘩眾取寵的題材」，希望民眾檢舉下架。<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/news/600/2020/04/09/phpfNbpiL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2Fnews%2F600%2F2020%2F04%2F09%2FphpfNbpiL.jpg&h=6ec95b0b&s={SIZE}\" /></div><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/health/breakingnews/3128305\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fhealth%2Fbreakingnews%2F3128305&d=6Nb1RK4hIZDTz%2Fb962ZojywbHaueoKb2XZOoGTcnCr8%3D&h=cabb8eb5\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fhealth%2Fbreakingnews%2F3128305&h=baaa2ff1\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/health/breakingnews/3128305</a>"},{"pid":"4ada07ab76560aa5f73be01d3bfdabfe959c248c","tid":1969522,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-12T13:03:30.000Z","msg":"小玉在影片中，先以戲謔語氣說「大家一定早就忘記媽媽的奶是什麼味道，除非你有很變態的癖好」，「你就看到那個成分，你就知道這東西其實味道......嗯......其實並不好」。<br />\n<br />\n影片中小玉打開購買的母乳聞了聞笑說「有一種工業的塑膠味，聞起來不臭，還可以」，接著試喝過程數度嘔吐，更指「很像豆漿又有一點臭掉的味道，很淡很淡加水加超多的那種杏仁茶，然後又有一點壞掉」「太臭了，有狗味，家裡有養吉娃娃都會有那個味道，就是吉娃娃家的味道，超級難喝的」。<br />\n<br />\n母乳協會直指，小玉所發布的的影片「真的是一支令人不舒服、戲謔、又未能傳達正確母乳知識的影片」，也向沒有哺乳經驗的女性喊話，「希望看到影片但還未曾哺乳的你要知道，那些影片中對母乳的味道、性狀負面的形象都不是事實，請不要因此對哺乳這件事感到退縮害怕」。"},{"pid":"46969d13cf42b618f0f957a5c84ae540e26bd1b7","tid":1969522,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-12T13:03:40.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=GtApzkekuUo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DGtApzkekuUo&d=6Nb1RK4hIZDTz%2Fb962ZojywbHaueoKb2XZOoGTcnCr8%3D&h=aac2d863\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=GtApzkekuUo</a>"},{"pid":"dd36df7e16132d5d528d94b55ecd34550a21c0b1","tid":1969522,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-12T13:04:06.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=KwzGEyTUNTc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DKwzGEyTUNTc&d=6Nb1RK4hIZDTz%2Fb962ZojywbHaueoKb2XZOoGTcnCr8%3D&h=7061081a\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=KwzGEyTUNTc</a>"},{"pid":"f49f5048a8efe51b6061e5b2ffe174c3ace36115","tid":1969522,"uid":1712,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-12T13:08:15.000Z","msg":"完全諗唔明呢條友點解會紅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"df08bcd448d242a4b9c159b757e9a029100dbbe5","tid":1969522,"uid":110988,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-12T13:46:55.000Z","msg":"D奶假架!<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8a8003aa36092b575c4c2bac70a2f968a6e25f47","tid":1969522,"uid":55458,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-12T13:49:21.000Z","msg":"母乳都有協會？<br />\n精液有冇？"},{"pid":"5a38cbf6ae11bc3a4d4fba199741b5478adb6094","tid":1969522,"uid":80560,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-12T13:50:21.000Z","msg":"噁心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}